### SQLMap Cheatsheet

| Goal | Command |
|------|---------|
| Test URL for SQLi | `sqlmap -u <URL>` |
| Get all databases | `sqlmap -u <URL> --dbs` |
| Get tables from DB | `sqlmap -u <URL> -D <database> --tables` |
| Dump table data | `sqlmap -u <URL> -D <database> -T <table> --dump` |
| Test POST request | `sqlmap -r request.txt` |
| Beginner mode | `sqlmap --wizard` |
| Deep scan | add `--level=5` |

